results.deck: Marvelous AQL, formerly known as Marvelous Entertainment Inc. is a multinational corporation that produces video games.
results.description:
Founded in 1997 as Marvelous Entertainment Inc, they're best known for developing the Harvest Moon series, as well as publishing numerous third-party games such as Deadly Premonition, Half-Minute Hero and Muramasa: The Demon Blade.

In October 2011 they merged with AQ Interactive and Liveware to form Marvelous AQL. On June 17th 2012 a European division was opened in the UK named Marvelous AQL Europe.
